# define CHAIRS 5         /**/
typedef int semaphone;    /**/
semaphore customers = 0 ; /**/
semaphore barbers = 0 ;   /**/
semaphore mutex_waiting = 1 ;/**/
int waiting = 0 ;         /**/

void barber(void){
	while(true){          /**/
		P(customers);     /*-1*/
		P(mutex_waiting);
			waiting--;
		V(barbers);       /*+1*/
		V(mutex_waiting); 
		cut_hair();
	}	
}

void customers(void){
	while(true){
		P(mutex_waiting);
		if(waiting < CHAIRS){  /**/
			waiting++;
			V(customers);      /*+1*/
			V(mutex_waiting);
			P(barbers);        /*-1*/
			get_haircut();
		}else{                 /**/
			V(mutex_waiting);
		}
	}
}

void main(){
cobegin
	barber();
	customers();
coend
}
